    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>The tip of this narrow +3 rapier can be used as a mundane writing instrument, producing any color of ink the wielder desires. Once per day as a free action when the wielder confirms a critical hit against a creature with the Red Crusader's quill, she can inscribe an arcane mark on the creature. Once per month, the wielder can instead inscribe a mark of justice; this mark ends immediately if the wielder inscribes another mark of justice with the Red Crusader's quill.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +3 rapier</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Magic Arms and Armor, arcane mark, mark of justice, creator must worship Arazni</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>AP 141",
